snippet.title: Janaab-e-Aali Song Teaser | WAR 2 | Hrithik Roshan, NTR | Pritam, Sachet Tandon, Saaj Bhatt, Amitabh
snippet.description:
The dance WAR you’ve been waiting for is almost here. Here’s the tease... #JanaabeAali full song in theatres only!
#War2 releasing in Hindi, Telugu and Tamil in cinemas worldwide on 14th August.

► Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/xs3mrY 🔔 Stay updated!
► YRF New Releases - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLCB05E03DA939D484

🎧 Song Credits:
Music: Pritam
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Singers: Sachet Tandon, Saaj Bhatt
Director of Choreography: Bosco Leslie Martis
Recording Studio: YRF Studios

Stay in the filmy loop:
► Like us on Facebook: Facebook/yrf 
► Follow us on X: x.com/yrf
► Follow us on Instagram: Instagram/yrf
► Visit us on: yashrajfilms.com

🎬 MOVIE CREDITS:
Movie: WAR 2
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, NTR, Kiara Advani
Director: Ayan Mukerji
Producer: Aditya Chopra
Co-Producer: Akshaye Widhani
Screenplay: Shridhar Raghavan
Director of Photography: Benjamin Jasper ACS

Visual Effects Studio: yFX

Supervising Producer: Gurpreet Singh
Trailers & Promos: Mohit Sajnaney
Release Date: 14 August 2025

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.description:
Celebrate the eternal bond of love and care this Raksha Bandhan with the heart-touching song "Behna O Pyari Behna" 🎶✨. Featuring Chunky Pandey, this emotional melody sung by the soulful  Shabbir Kumar, Bablu, Sadhana Sargam, perfectly captures the love between a brother and sister. ❤️👫

Singers : Shabbir Kumar, Bablu, Sadhana Sargam

snippet.title: Andhera Season 1 - Official Trailer | Prajakta Koli, Surveen Chawla, Priya Bapat, Karanvir Malhotra
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Andhera Season 1 Official Trailer
Starring Priya Bapat, Karanvir Malhotra, Prajakta Koli, Surveen Chawla, Vatsal Sheth, Parvin Dabas, Pranay Pachauri
Directed by Raaghav Dar
Written by Gaurav Desai, Raaghav Dar, Karan Anshuman, Chintan
Sarda, Akshat Ghildial, Karmanya Ahuja
Created by Gaurav Desai
Executive Producers: Ritesh Sidhwani, Farhan Akhtar, Kassim
Jagmagia, Mohit Shah, Karan Anshuman
Associate Producer: Vishal Ramchandani
Production Company: Excel Media and Entertainment LLP

Official Release Date Aug 14 2025, on Prime Video India.

About:
In the shadow of Mumbai's shimmering skyline, a sinister force
hunts the living. In this visceral tale of urban horror, a fearless cop
and a haunted medical student must take on this living darkness
to avert impending doom.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: Phaphey Kuttniyan (Movie Trailer) | Neeru Bajwa | Tania | New Punjabi Movie 2025 | Speed Records
snippet.description:
The trailer of ‘Phaphey Kuttniyan’, presented by Speed Records, offers a sneak peek into what promises to be one of the most entertaining Punjabi movies of 2025. Starring powerhouse performers Neeru Bajwa and Tania, the film blends humour, emotion, and drama rooted in the colourful chaos.

Directed with a refreshing take on comedy, Phaphey Kuttniyan is set to deliver laughs and life lessons in equal measure. The chemistry between the lead actresses, paired with a vibrant supporting cast, makes this trailer a must-watch for fans of Punjabi cinema. If you love films that balance tradition, emotion, and clever comedy, this one’s for your 2025 watchlist.

snippet.title: Sri Varalakshmi Mangala Harathi Telugu | Sravanam Sukravaram Special | Lakshmi Devi Songs
snippet.description:
🌺 Sri Varalakshmi Mangala Harathi – A sacred and melodious Telugu devotional song dedicated to Goddess VaraLakshmi Devi, the goddess of wealth, prosperity, and auspiciousness.

Sri Varalakshmi Mangala Harathi Telugu,Varalakshmi Vratham Songs,Goddess Lakshmi Harathi,Sravana Sukravaram Special Songs,Lakshmi Devi Devotional Songs Telugu,Mangala Harathi Telugu Songs,Lakshmi Bhakti Songs,Varalakshmi Pooja Harathi,Friday Lakshmi Pooja Songs,Sravana Masam Special Bhakti Songs,Lakshmi Songs for Pooja,Telugu Devotional Songs for Goddess Lakshmi,Lakshmi Devi Songs Telugu,SriVaralakshmiMangalaHarathi,VaralakshmiDeviSongs,SravanamSukravaramSpecial

Lyrics:Traditioanl
Composer: Ghatti Sri Vidya
Singer: Ghatti Srividya

This divine Harathi song is specially offered on Sravana Sukravaram (Fridays in the month of Sravana), which holds immense spiritual significance in South Indian tradition. It is believed that offering Mangala Harathi to Varalakshmi Devi on this auspicious day brings blessings of Dhana (wealth), Dhanya (food), and Arogya (health).

🪔 Use this beautiful song during your Varalakshmi Vratham Pooja, Friday Lakshmi Pooja, or daily prayers to invoke the grace of Mahalakshmi.

🎧 Listen, chant, and share this soulful song with all devotees and make your spiritual Fridays even more divine.

snippet.description:
रक्षाबंधन स्पेशल 2025 ~ आया राखी का त्यौहार | Nonstop Raksha Bandhan Songs | भाई बहन का गीत #shivanikathumka #shivanirakshabandhansong

🎙️ प्रिय श्रोताओ, आप सभी का हार्दिक स्वागत है हमारे चैनल — "देहाती भक्ति भजन" पर।
यहाँ आपको मिलेंगे गाँव की मिट्टी से जुड़े सच्चे सुर, लोकगीत , देशभक्ति गीत ,राधा-कृष्ण की झांकियाँ, और देसी अंदाज़ में गाए गए है

🙏 भक्ति में लीन होइए, चैनल को सब्सक्राइब कीजिए, 
👉 Subscribe Now : https://goo.gl/FQHcHM
और हमारे साथ जुड़िए इस आध्यात्मिक यात्रा में।
 हर हफ्ते 2 नयी झांकिया और भजनों के लिए बेल🔔आइकन जरूर दबाएं।

Enjoy & Stay Related Videos : 
👉 https://youtu.be/UNkkcCvDYSQ?si=qDBxt4CPhR4WlHz8
👉 https://youtu.be/Osp9X_7MDII?si=M_LylmwUebeiaLkh
👉 https://youtu.be/E6xlraIR1B4?si=la0fuo36tpZUc3GW
👉 https://youtu.be/WjdODhy9MEw?si=QRTWmcCNE5LvJIOE
👉https://youtu.be/CybOSmab66A?si=yUlt0c8Sh4Bc78uC

🎉 रक्षा बंधन – एक पवित्र बंधन का त्योहार 🎉
रक्षा बंधन हर वर्ष श्रावण मास की पूर्णिमा तिथि को मनाया जाता है। यह आमतौर पर जुलाई-अगस्त के महीने में आता है।
🪢 क्या है रक्षा बंधन?
रक्षा बंधन एक ऐसा पर्व है जो भाई-बहन के प्रेम, सुरक्षा, और कर्तव्य के बंधन को समर्पित होता है। इस दिन बहन अपने भाई की कलाई पर राखी बाँधती है और उसकी लंबी उम्र की कामना करती है। बदले में भाई अपनी बहन को जीवनभर उसकी रक्षा करने का वचन देता है।
🧵 राखी का महत्व:
"रक्षा" का अर्थ है सुरक्षा और "बंधन" का अर्थ है बंधन या संबंध।
राखी केवल धागा नहीं बल्कि विश्वास, प्रेम और सुरक्षा का प्रतीक होती है।
यह एक धार्मिक और सांस्कृतिक परंपरा है जो समय के साथ और भी मजबूत होती चली आ रही है।
🛐 धार्मिक और ऐतिहासिक मान्यता:
भगवान कृष्ण और द्रौपदी:
महाभारत में, जब श्रीकृष्ण ने अपनी उँगली काटी थी, तब द्रौपदी ने अपनी साड़ी का टुकड़ा फाड़कर उनकी उँगली में बाँधा था। श्रीकृष्ण ने इसे राखी का रूप मानकर द्रौपदी को हमेशा रक्षा का वचन दिया।
राजा बलि और माता लक्ष्मी:
भगवान विष्णु ने वचन के अनुसार राजा बलि के पास वामन रूप में रहने का निर्णय लिया। तब माता लक्ष्मी ने बलि को राखी बाँधी और विष्णु जी को वापस ले आईं।
🪔 रक्षा बंधन की परंपरा:
बहन भाई की आरती करती है, तिलक लगाती है, मिठाई खिलाकर राखी बांधती है।
भाई बहन को उपहार, पैसे या कोई वस्तु देता है।
फिर दोनों एक-दूसरे की लंबी उम्र और खुशहाल जीवन की कामना करते हैं।
🌍 भारत और विदेशों में रक्षा बंधन:
भारत के हर राज्य में इसे अलग-अलग तरीकों से मनाया जाता है।
नेपाल, मॉरीशस, फिजी, अमेरिका, कनाडा जैसे देशों में बसे भारतीय भी इसे उत्साह से मनाते हैं।
💖 रक्षा बंधन का संदेश:
रक्षा बंधन सिर्फ भाई-बहन के रिश्ते तक सीमित नहीं है, बल्कि यह प्यार, भरोसे और कर्तव्य का प्रतीक है। यह त्योहार मानवता और रिश्तों की मिठास को मजबूत करता है।

2-JKB-DHT-SKT

शिवानी के रक्षाबंधन गीत

snippet.title: COOLIE Trailer Reaction! With Vivan & Brandon | Rajinikanth | Nagarjuna Akkineni | Aamir Khan
snippet.description:
Vivan and Brandon react to the explosive trailer for Coolie, marking the fiery return of Rajinikanth in a mass-loaded, emotional action drama.

Directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj (Leo, Vikram), Coolie brings back Rajinikanth (Jailer, Kaala) in a powerful new avatar—mixing grit, style, and legacy. With Anirudh Ravichander’s pulse-pounding score and stunning visuals, the film promises high-octane action and deep-rooted emotion.

Vivan and Brandon break down the intensity, vintage Rajini swag, and Lokesh’s signature world-building. Coolie looks like a full-blown cinematic celebration of one of India’s biggest icons.

____________________

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQeljbfXMX_5a2_KMXTkF-A/join

snippet.title: Vhala Aavo Gokul Gam - 4K Video - Gopal Bharwad - Jigar Studio
snippet.description:
Song: Vhala Aavo Gokul Gam
Singer: Gopal Bharwad
Artists: Vijay Desai, Aarti Suthar, Hemali Gohil, Sanjay Pandya, Hasmukh Limbachiya
Music: Vishal Vagheshwari, Sunil Vagheshwari
Lyrics: Sahar Rabari
BGM: Rajendrasinh
Co - Ordinator: Indar Gamara
D.O.P. - Edit: Montu Rajput
Director: Vishnu Thakor - Adalaj
Producer: Gunvant Thakor
Music Label & Copyright: Jigar Studio

Lyrics Of This Song:

Kok Di Aavo Gokuliye Gam
Ke Kano Aaj Hambhare Chhe
He Vhala Aavo Gokuliye Gam
Ke Aaj Kano Hambhare Chhe
He Rove Chodhare Aakhuy Gam
Ke Kanho Kyare Aave Chhe
Ae Balpana Ni Gothano Ni Maya Meli Re
Kon Amaru Thashe Tara Vagar Meli Re
Vage Vage Hatey Hara Na Sur
Toye Pag Na Upade Re
He Mane Rahade Ramade Kon
Ke Kanho Aaj Hambhare Chhe

Pan Hari, Ae Hari Vagar Aa Het Kya Vechava
Are Re Mara Gani Ne Karya Te Vegada
Are Re Te To Karya Chhe Aaj Vegada
He Melya Kaleje Pana Na Bhar
Ke Yaad Tari Kanade Chhe
He Bhale Lakho Var Bhuliye Tara Nam
Toye Kajale Lay Lage Chhe
Amara Rakhya Ma Khot Kya Khataki Re
Hachu Na Bolo To Gala Na Ham Tamane
He Vhala Aavo Vrundavan Aaj
Maro Kano Mane Hambhare Chhe
Nidhivane Gopiyu Juve Tari Vat
Kanudo Aaj Hambhare Chhe

Pan Ame Dahya, Ae Dahya Ganda Thai Fariye
Are Re Hau Ne Jivataye Mua Lagiye
Are Re Ame Jivata Pan Mua Lagiye
He Aaj Mota Lai Betho Hashe Kam
Ke Kal Kanho Aavashe Re
Ha Eva Dal Ne Dalaha Dai
Aa Dan Mara Jay Chhe Re
Barsana Dungar Jovu Vatadi Re
Hu To Dungariye Chadi Jovu Vatadi Re
He Kanji Kanji Kari Modha Hukay
Pan Kanho Kya Hambhare Chhe
Tane To Badhu Hasya Ma Jay
Ahiya Jiv Maro Jay Chhe Re
Ha Eto Vite Ene Vedanayu Thay
Makhan Na Morari Re
Ha Kevi Munjhani Hashu Man Ma
Barsana Jovu Vatadi Re

snippet.title: Chhoti Bhen 2 (Lyrical Video) | Shubham Mahi | Raksha Bandhan Special 2025
snippet.description:
Chhoti Bhen 2 (Lyrical Video) | Shubham Mahi | Raksha Bandhan Special 2025

Chhoti Bhen 2 (Lyrical Video) | Shubham Mahi | Raksha Bandhan Special 2025

#chhotibhen #chotibhen #rakshabandhan #sistersongs #sisterbrothersong

Song : Chhoti Bhen 2
Singer : Shubham Mahi
Lyrics : Assandhwala Armaan
Music : Shakti Music
Video : Abhishek Kumar
Lable : @LaybaMusic

तू ए तो सै म्हारे इस घर की रौनक 
होया कर ना उदास मेरी सांस थम जा
तेरे भाई की सै जान बस तेरे मैं बसा
मेरे कहऩ की नी लोड़ तू सब समझा
तेरी हर एक करूंगा ख्वाहिश मै पूरी
बस कैम रवा तेरी मुस्कान री
छोटी बहन मेरी बोल का तो देख तू
तेरे कदमा मा रख दु जहान री

तने क्यूकर बताऊं यो बहन भाई का 
जो रिश्ता सै बड़ा अनमोल होवा सै 
एक भाई ने होवा सै बहन जान ते भी प्यारी
बस मुंह ते कदे ना लाडो बोल होवा सै
तू चहकती रवा तो घर लागे मने घर
ईंट पत्थर का नहीं तो मकान री
छोटी बहन मेरी बोल का तो देख तू
तेरे कदमा मा रख दु जहान री

दुनिया मा सबते जो प्यारी चीज कोई
रब ने बनाई वो बहन होवा सै
पूरी जिंदगी लुटा दे भाई बहन की खुशी मै
बाद उसके भी भाई ने ना चैन होवा सै
कदे आंच भी ना तेरे पा री आण मै देऊँ 
तेरी खुशियां पा वार दूं यो जान री 
छोटी बहन मेरी बोल का तो देख तू
तेरे कदमा मा रख दु जहान री

तेरा दिल जो कहवा सै कर नहीं टोकता
बस बाप की तू पगड़ी का ख्याल राखिए 
धूम धाम ते करूं मै तेरी डोली ने विदा
बस इतने से बोल ये सम्भाल राखिए
रब्ब करे तेरे होवे सारे सपने री पूरे
असंधवाले का सै यो ही अरमान री
छोटी बहन मेरी बोल का तो देख तू
तेरे कदमा मा रख दु जहान री

snippet.title: Radhika Dulari (Official Video) | Indresh Upadhyay | B Praak | Mir Desai | Feat. Adrija Roy
snippet.description:
🌸 Radhika Dulari 🌸
A divine expression of longing, love, and surrender. This is not just a song - it is a celebration of Prem Bhakti. Indresh Upadhyay Ji lends his devotional voice to a heartfelt music by B Praak and Mir Desai and beautifully inacted by Adrija Roy. 

Singer - Indresh Upadhyay Ji
Music - Bpraak & Mir Desai
Lyricist - Ravindra Jain
Feat. - Adrija Roy 

Music production and arrangement - Mir Desai 
Flute - Kiran Vinkar 
Guitars - Ishan Das
All instruments recorded @Midnightowl studios
Mixed and Mastered by Hanish Taneja @Studio Alika

Video Director - Prateek Thakur 
Editor - Mayank Thapar 
DOP - Kaustubh Nagar
Assistant Cinematographer - Jella
Gaffer - Devender
Colorist - Manish Panghal
VFX - Gagan Matharoo

Creatives & Artwork - Uday Kushwah
https://www.instagram.com/dreamdzign/

Line Producer - Lucky Tomar
Production Manager - Yogesh Tomar
Assistant Production Manager - RDX Aryan Choudhary
Location Manager - Durg Singh Thakur 

Special Thanks to - Karuna Sharma and Kunwar Kishor Premnidhi

Art - Dilip Nishad
Travel - M.J. Tours & Travels
Spot - Chote Lal

Digital Distribution - Universal Music
Project Head - Sahil Sharma and Anshool Uttamani 

#Radhikadulari #KripaRecords #DevotionalMusic #indreshupadhyay  #Radha #Krishna  #Vrindavan #Bpraak #Barsana 

(c) Universal Music Group

► About Kripa Records:

"Kripa Records" is a devotional music label dedicated to producing and promoting spiritual music that inspires profound experiences. "Kripa" meaning "grace" in Sanskrit, reflects the essence of divine mercy in the label's music. Kripa’s diverse devotional music is crafted by renowned artists, invoking peace, reverence, and spiritual awakening. It will serve as a cherished companion for meditation, prayer, and reflection.

snippet.title: Aage Bhai Rakhi आगे भाई राखी | New Cg Rakhi Song | Sarla Gandharw | रक्षाबंधन गीत Chhattisgarhi Gana
snippet.description:
#cgsong #cgsong2025  #newcgsong #cgdjsong #ChhattisgarhiGana #avmgana #rakhi #chhattisgarhisong 

Aage Bhai Rakhi आगे भाई राखी | Cg Song | Sarla Gandharw | रक्षाबंधन गीत Karan Chauhan | छत्तीसगढ़ी नया गाना | Damini Gandharw | Raksha Bandhan Special Song 2025 | Virendra Thakur | सीजी सॉन्ग न्यू | Chhattisgarhi Gana | AVMGANA | AVM STUDIO RAIPUR 

Song    -  Aage Bhai Rakhi 
Singer  -   Sarla Gandharw
Lyrics  -  Sarla Gandharw
Producer  -   Santosh Kurrey
Director  -  Deepak Kurrey
Artist -   Karan Chauhan, Damini Gandharw, Virendra Thakur
Camera  Saroj Kurrey
Choreographer - Kiran Chauhan
Editor  -   Narottam Mahant 
Makeup -  Bhumi Sidar, Suman Divya
Graphics -  Sandhya Chhatriya, Renuka Sahu
Youtube -  Ashok Kurrey
Recording - AVM Audio & Video Studio, Khamtarai, Raipur (C.G)
Recordist - Rakesh Kurrey , Ravi Kurrey - 09301523929
Audio Mastring - Santosh Kurrey
Contact for Recording - AVM Audio & Video Studio, Near L.I.C. Building Shree Nagar  Khamtarai, Raipur (C.G) MO - 09301523929



Humare Avm Gana Channel mein Chhatishgarhi Hits Gana aap logo ke liye prastut karte hain. Hum Chahte hain ki har baar aapke pasand ka New Cg Song aap logo ko de. 
Hume apne comment me bataye Chhattisgarhi Geet kisake aawaz me sunana chahte avam video dekhana chahte hain. Hum Humare gana ko Dj Version mein bhi layenge, hum humare Avm Gana Me hit chhattisgarhi gana dene ke liye pratibaddh hain. 
Hum humare Chhattisgarhi geet ko badhava dene wale singer & actor Tijan bai, Usha Barle, Mamta Chandrakar, Anuj sharma, Nitin Dubey, Dilip shadangi, Alka Chandrakar, chaya Chandrakar, Bhupendra sahu, Mithilesh sahu, Kuleshwar tamrakar , Kavita Vaishanvi, Sunil Soni,
Kanchan joshi, Sarla Gandharw, Anupma mishra, Sunny pandey, Dilip Ray, Shashi Rangila, Virendra Chaturvedi, Shyam Kuteliya, Karan Chauhan, Kiran Chauhan, Monika Verma, Seema Kaushik, Gorelal Barman, Garima Diwakar, Dilip Lahariya, Devesh Dahariya
Mann Quereshi, Anikriti Chauhan, Amlesh Nagesh, isi tarah chhattisgarh ke hum sabhi any singer avam actor ko tahe dil se Dhanywaad Karte hain. Jo Humari Chhattisgarhi Boli ko Desh va Videsh me Badhava De Rahe Hain...

The one and only TUNG TUNG TUNG SAHUR is the main villain — and he’s ready to crush ANY superhero that gets in his way!

🚁 Helicopters twisting through traps
